description:
When adding a keypair to nova using the following:
  euca-add-keypair keyname
Then repeating that command
  euca-add-keypair keyname
produces an Unknown Error exception and the stack trace below
See: http://paste.openstack.org/show/1197/

Ubuntu 10.10 amd64
Version from ppa: 2011.2~gamma2~bzr989-0ubuntu0ppa1~maverick1
euca2ools 1.2-0ubuntu11.1
title: Adding a keypair that already exists produces an Unknown error
